Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.63,0:00:03.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今年也是美好的一年呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.56,0:00:06.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在今年的最后 还是要做「那个」才行吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.72,0:00:07.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,做「那个」？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.54,0:00:09.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,美好的一年要结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.98,0:00:12.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爱丽丝…这么一想确实会让人感到寂寞
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.98,0:00:16.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但心中的美好是永远都不会消失的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.20,0:00:17.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让人害羞的台词 禁止！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.21,0:00:38.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小爱 今天是24月31日 天晴 有时下雪
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.72,0:00:42.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我来到AQUA后的第二个除夕夜就要到了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.71,0:00:52.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好冷 可是空气很舒服呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.87,0:00:56.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在AQUA度过的第二个春夏秋冬里
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.07,0:01:01.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我所度过的每一天都如同宝物般闪闪发光
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.55,0:01:07.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,顺带一提 在地球上圣诞节是大家一起过
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.62,0:01:10.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,除夕则是与家人一起过的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.90,0:01:12.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在新威尼斯却相反
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.26,0:01:14.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟家人一起过圣诞节
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.96,0:01:16.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟朋友一起过除夕才是主流
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.57,0:01:19.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以今天我们要去圣马可广场
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.16,0:01:21.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟大家一起过除夕
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.67,0:01:26.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么办…艾莉西亚前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.08,0:01:28.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了？灯里
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.08,0:01:31.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今年我也好兴奋哦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.51,0:01:32.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.82,0:03:24.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鬓子好慢啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.89,0:03:30.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亏人家这么早来帮艾莉西亚小姐占位置
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.74,0:03:32.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,晓
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.84,0:03:35.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,晓先生 伍迪先生
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.25,0:03:39.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起 我来晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.95,0:03:42.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不会不会 快请坐吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.58,0:03:45.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我早已为艾莉西亚小姐占好座位了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.06,0:03:48.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀哎呀 谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.47,0:03:50.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小爱
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.69,0:03:52.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,新威尼斯的除夕
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.61,0:03:55.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全城的人都会聚集到圣马可广场
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.75,0:03:59.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,主要活动是新年倒数
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.76,0:04:03.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后一直到新年日出之时
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.76,0:04:07.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人们都会为庆祝新年而彻夜狂欢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.86,0:04:10.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有在这个时候 大家才会不拘礼节
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.09,0:04:14.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,简直就是喧闹而盛大的祭典
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.18,0:04:21.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真想让小爱也来这里看看…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.82,0:04:24.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 所以我来看了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.58,0:04:25.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.69,0:04:28.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我刚才好像听到小爱的声音了…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.06,0:04:30.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.28,0:04:33.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,灯里 我来啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.09,0:04:40.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亚利亚社长 好久不见
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.22,0:04:43.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.70,0:04:49.63,TITLE,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(1000,0)\pos(320,270)\blur9\be1\fsp2}那个 纯白的早晨…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.62,0:04:55.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦～ 艾莉西亚前辈知道小爱要来啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.80,0:05:00.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 想给灯里一个惊喜 就没告诉你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.78,0:05:03.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我跟艾莉西亚也是朋友哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.05,0:05:10.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,话说 你姐姐他们呢？是一起来的吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.38,0:05:10.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.27,0:05:14.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐会在天亮的时候来接我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.03,0:05:19.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐夫笃井因为工作关系要明天下午才来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.29,0:05:22.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我们就能一起过除夕了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.79,0:05:23.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.76,0:05:27.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 鬓子 这个小不点女孩是谁？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.26,0:05:31.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊～ 你是气候调节员晓先生
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.94,0:05:34.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是空中邮递员伍迪先生
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.44,0:05:36.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么你认识我们？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.84,0:05:37.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么的说？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.12,0:05:39.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从灯里的邮件里知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.05,0:05:40.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,邮件？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.95,0:05:41.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘿嘿
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.24,0:05:45.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,灯里 晓先生很帅气呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.54,0:05:45.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.12,0:05:47.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦？是嘛是嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.41,0:05:52.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,气候调节员为了让AQUA的人们过得舒适
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.64,0:05:55.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而在浮岛上每日奋战着呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.56,0:05:58.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错 气候调节员是正义的英雄哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.25,0:06:02.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过你在哥哥面前总是抬不起头来吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.50,0:06:03.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.40,0:06:04.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为欠哥哥的钱
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.11,0:06:05.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.27,0:06:07.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小爱…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.32,0:06:08.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鬓子啊…！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.47,0:06:12.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是个可爱的孩子的说
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.33,0:06:13.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哪里可爱了？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.21,0:06:16.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,交到个可爱的女朋友了嘛 弟弟啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.30,0:06:18.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大哥…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.34,0:06:21.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊～ 是晓先生的哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.74,0:06:22.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哪里可…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.26,0:06:24.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样就找到第三个人了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.48,0:06:27.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小爱 找到…？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.75,0:06:31.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,找到了灯里邮件中出现的人物
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.52,0:06:33.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真高兴啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.26,0:06:35.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.83,0:06:40.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.66,0:06:42.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把手伸出来好吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.12,0:06:43.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,手？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.45,0:06:45.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.51,0:06:52.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.59,0:06:55.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是用新威尼斯玻璃制作的豆子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.37,0:06:56.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,豆子？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.24,0:07:00.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,豆子象征着财富 据说能带来幸运
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.39,0:07:04.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在地球上的意大利
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.41,0:07:08.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有年末一定要吃豆子料理的习惯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.75,0:07:11.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,据说这个城市也继承了那个传统
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.98,0:07:15.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过玻璃做的豆子不能吃呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.92,0:07:20.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是观光的礼物啦 很受欢迎的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.60,0:07:25.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要弄丢了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.26,0:07:26.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs26}别掉了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.65,0:07:29.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如何？是不是有种幸福将要来临的感觉？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.12,0:07:34.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当作你跟我任性的弟弟这么要好的谢礼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.97,0:07:35.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就收下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.18,0:07:37.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么要好啊…喂…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.81,0:07:41.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你 叔叔
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.74,0:07:43.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,叔…叔叔？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.39,0:07:47.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呵呵…叔叔啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.86,0:07:51.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我先走一步了 再会了 淑女们
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.89,0:07:55.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥好像比你更帅气…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.58,0:07:57.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.86,0:08:00.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 大家都到齐啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.80,0:08:03.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾莉西亚前辈～ 晚安～
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.75,0:08:07.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小爱 你怎么会在这里？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.73,0:08:10.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想跟大家一起过除夕 就跑来了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.95,0:08:14.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么远的距离 你可真有心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.11,0:08:16.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蓝华 这孩子是？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.24,0:08:19.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就是鬼教官晃小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.72,0:08:20.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鬼教官？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.85,0:08:22.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样就找到第四个人了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.07,0:08:24.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 蓝华！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.97,0:08:25.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是误会…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.99,0:08:29.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,灯里！你到底给小爱写的什么邮件啊！？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.67,0:08:31.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么样的…就是一般的邮件啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.98,0:08:32.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.11,0:08:34.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就是阿鲁先生？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.53,0:08:38.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的 初次见面 我就是重力调节员阿鲁
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.33,0:08:40.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯…重力调节员就是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.68,0:08:44.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在地下调节重力的工作…吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.06,0:08:46.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的 你说得没错
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.28,0:08:50.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个…有一件事很难启齿…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.33,0:08:51.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么事呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.56,0:08:53.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你对蓝华到底…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.14,0:08:54.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了！到此为止！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.43,0:08:58.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 灯里 那孩子会不会太兴奋了？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.43,0:08:59.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.40,0:09:00.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.36,0:09:02.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来 亚利亚社长 飞高高
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.49,0:09:04.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs26}飞啊飞啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.69,0:09:06.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她能够与原本只能从我的邮件中认识的人们见面
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.43,0:09:06.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs26}飞啊飞啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.63,0:09:11.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就像与小说中的登场人物直接见面了一样
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.92,0:09:13.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是件很让人高兴的事情啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.27,0:09:14.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让人害羞的台词 禁止！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.24,0:09:17.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家晚安
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.49,0:09:21.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祖母！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.68,0:09:22.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好久不见
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.24,0:09:24.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您最近安好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.14,0:09:29.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀 亚利亚社长
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.42,0:09:30.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,见到你这么有精神真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.12,0:09:31.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祖母
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.05,0:09:34.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您也来了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.45,0:09:37.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好久不见了 祖母
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.20,0:09:40.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀呀 大家都到齐了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.14,0:09:43.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家还是像以前这么要好 真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.47,0:09:44.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.27,0:09:47.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个人就是祖母吗 好棒
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.26,0:09:50.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是第六个人了 灯里
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.94,0:09:54.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀哎呀 是位可爱的小姐呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.09,0:09:56.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是灯里的朋友吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.01,0:10:00.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的 她是从地球来的 叫小爱
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.26,0:10:01.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,晚安 祖母
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.03,0:10:04.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,晚安 小爱
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.17,0:10:07.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祖母 请来这边坐
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.91,0:10:09.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你 蓝华
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.42,0:10:15.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 鬓子 那位贵妇人是谁？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.58,0:10:19.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那一位是创立了亚利亚公司的大前辈…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.75,0:10:24.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等 亚利亚社长
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.86,0:10:25.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小爱？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.82,0:10:26.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 鬓子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.81,0:10:27.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,灯里
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.51,0:10:28.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你去哪里？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.89,0:10:29.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我马上回来
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.34,0:10:31.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小爱 等等我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.90,0:10:37.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,社长
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.90,0:10:39.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亚利亚社长
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.72,0:10:42.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小爱 不要紧吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.37,0:10:45.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.93,0:10:56.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起…把亚利亚社长跟丢了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.90,0:10:58.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没问题的 你看
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.32,0:11:02.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走吧 小爱
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.84,0:11:03.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.07,0:11:18.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一片漆黑…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.44,0:11:21.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,足迹一直延伸到这里面哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.60,0:11:22.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.81,0:12:08.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.25,0:12:17.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,猫？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.65,0:12:19.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那只猫…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.23,0:12:38.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.38,0:12:43.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,信件真的能穿越时空 传达心意的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.16,0:12:47.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,据说猫是连接过去和未来的动物
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.55,0:13:01.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才的…难道是以前的AQUA？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.73,0:13:03.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯…大概是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.29,0:13:08.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真不可思议…总觉得…有种熟悉的感觉…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.58,0:13:10.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.47,0:13:15.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也是…虽然是完全不了解的时代
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.43,0:13:20.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道说 我受到AQUA的欢迎了？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.23,0:13:27.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 一定是这样的 小爱
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.08,0:13:31.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那真是让人高兴呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.38,0:13:36.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亚利亚社长？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.06,0:13:41.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是什么东西在发光？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.29,0:13:46.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道说…果然破了个洞
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.29,0:13:50.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,东西都掉出去了 什么时候破的…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.38,0:13:52.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.66,0:13:54.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就是说 只要顺着这些光走
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.81,0:13:56.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就能回到原来的地方了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.36,0:14:00.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊！是光的路标呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.93,0:14:03.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 我们一边捡一边回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.89,0:14:04.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.94,0:14:11.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,灯里前辈她们好慢啊 不会出什么事吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.00,0:14:13.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不久就会回来的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.93,0:14:15.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她们一定是到处去逛了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.10,0:14:17.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.20,0:14:21.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.44,0:14:24.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,欢迎回来 灯里 小爱
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.71,0:14:26.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们跑哪里去了啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.40,0:14:27.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯…那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.60,0:14:32.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,AQUA
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.66,0:14:35.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在说什么啊？AQUA不就是这里嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.26,0:14:37.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,超级不知所云
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.82,0:14:43.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了 小爱 你带了什么可以扔的东西吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.37,0:14:44.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以扔的东西？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.79,0:14:47.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,新威尼斯除夕最盛大的活动
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.72,0:14:49.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是在新年的凌晨零点
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.35,0:14:51.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一起用力把什么东西扔向天空
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.22,0:14:54.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要是去年使用过的东西 什么都可以
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.26,0:14:57.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,灯里要扔什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.64,0:14:59.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们领航员都是扔这个
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.80,0:15:02.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我…扔这个
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.87,0:15:07.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个缎带是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.29,0:15:09.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 上次来的时候系的缎带
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.16,0:15:12.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为要来新威尼斯 所以就系上它了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.18,0:15:15.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗？很有纪念意义的缎带呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.39,0:15:23.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,差不多要开始倒数了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.26,0:15:31.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小爱 新年的庆贺语是AUGURI BUON ANNO
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.00,0:15:34.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,AUGURI…BUON ANNO？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.60,0:15:37.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 AUGURI是祝贺的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.49,0:15:41.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,BUON ANNO则是新年快乐的意思
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.64,0:15:42.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.43,0:15:48.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今年真的发生了许多事情
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.97,0:15:53.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,美丽的邂逅 和独一无二的美好时光
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.46,0:15:55.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样的一年…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.82,0:16:00.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了？灯里
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.01,0:16:05.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一想到这像宝物一样闪闪发光的一年
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.30,0:16:08.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,马上就要结束了…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.35,0:16:11.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总觉得有点让人感伤
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.09,0:16:13.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让…让人害羞的…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.95,0:16:17.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我真是个奢侈的人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.14,0:16:18.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.12,0:16:20.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,美好的奢侈呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.04,0:16:22.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}dieci(10)
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.37,0:16:23.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}nove(9)
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.74,0:16:24.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}otto(8)
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.14,0:16:26.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}sette(7)
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.42,0:16:27.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}sei(6)
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.61,0:16:28.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}cinque(5)
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.92,0:16:29.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}quattro(4)
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.23,0:16:31.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}tre(3)
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.45,0:16:32.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}due(2)
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.62,0:16:34.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}uno(1)！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.60,0:16:26.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,灯里
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.58,0:16:27.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 小爱
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.52,0:16:39.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,AUGURI BUON ANNO！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.99,0:17:56.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早安 灯里 小爱
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.74,0:17:59.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早安
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.46,0:18:01.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知不觉就睡着了呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.62,0:18:04.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也是刚刚才醒的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.35,0:18:06.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小爱 看看后面
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.51,0:18:09.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.84,0:18:11.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我来接你了 爱
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.97,0:18:13.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小爱的姐姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.58,0:18:14.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 请坐在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.91,0:18:16.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你 灯里
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.45,0:18:18.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过我一坐下这孩子就会哭的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.40,0:18:20.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.07,0:18:24.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,初次见面 她的名字是？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.13,0:18:26.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她叫做 AQUA（水星）
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.00,0:18:27.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,AQUA？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.18,0:18:29.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好棒的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.95,0:18:30.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.60,0:18:32.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,AQUA啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.25,0:18:42.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀哎呀 AQUA真厉害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.62,0:18:52.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想跟这孩子一起看
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.16,0:18:55.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我最喜欢的AQUA的新年日出
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.62,0:19:03.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看啊 AQUA 太阳要升起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.52,0:19:15.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是新年日出
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.87,0:19:18.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太阳的光芒让人感觉到了温暖
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.07,0:19:22.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像连内心深处也被温暖了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.72,0:19:24.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让人害羞的台词 禁止！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.90,0:19:26.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.99,0:19:30.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希望今年也是美好的一年
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.42,0:19:32.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定会的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.03,0:19:34.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也这么认为
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.01,0:19:35.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.58,0:19:37.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾莉西亚前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.66,0:19:40.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我今年也会为了成为
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.77,0:19:41.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,独当一面的领航员而努力的！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.02,0:19:44.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蓝华 这种话应该跟我说！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.43,0:19:45.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.06,0:19:53.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用全身去感受阳光
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.71,0:19:57.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,异常耀眼而崭新的 纯白的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.78,0:20:00.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 是个崭新的 暖洋洋的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.51,0:20:02.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,纯白的一年的初始之日啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.04,0:20:05.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这以后的世界将被染成什么样的色彩
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.98,0:20:07.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就看我们了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.71,0:20:08.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.46,0:20:15.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 爱 我们该回酒店了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.34,0:20:17.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要好好地睡一觉才行
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.18,0:20:21.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为下午还要跟笃井姐夫会合呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.91,0:20:23.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再见了 灯里
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.72,0:20:25.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 再见了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.22,0:20:25.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再见
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.22,0:20:27.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再见
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.63,0:20:29.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再会的说
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.13,0:20:32.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,路上小心
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.09,0:20:47.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小爱跟她姐姐看起来很幸福呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.69,0:20:50.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾莉西亚前辈跟小爱的姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.12,0:20:53.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是在她来水星做新婚旅行的时候见过的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.48,0:20:54.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.29,0:20:59.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小宝贝比照相的时候长大了许多呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.64,0:21:01.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很可爱呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.40,0:21:06.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她能带着孩子一起来 真是令人高兴呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.05,0:21:11.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 没想到再次相会时彼此的家人都增加了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.65,0:21:12.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.84,0:21:13.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.85,0:21:16.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦…彼此？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.17,0:21:32.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,灯里…AUGURI BUON ANNO
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.10,0:21:40.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾莉西亚前辈 AUGURI BUON ANNO
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.76,0:21:44.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今年也请多关照
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.22,0:21:49.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我才是 要请你多多关照
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.63,0:22:05.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对创造了这个美好的星球的人们…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.49,0:22:10.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也对在这美好的星球上共度时光的人们…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.87,0:22:14.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,同时也对这个美好的星球 AQUA…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.57,0:22:18.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也是对将要邂逅的你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.04,0:22:21.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,内心满怀感激之情
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.68,0:22:24.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,AUGURI BUON ANNO
